<br>
Smithing considers one out of these 3 stats (whichever one is higher):  Int, Wis, Str.  It has been suggested (and may be incoming in a patch) that tailoring and fletching may go to 3 stats:  Int, Wis, Dex.<br>
<br>
Secondary stats have never been confirmed (nor denied by even me).  However, having a primary stat (Int/Wis) at 255 makes learning any tradeskill go a whole lot easier.<br>
